== 制作 ==
编剧张建伟曾是《[[走向共和|走向共和]]》和《[[军人机密|军人机密]]》的编剧；马伊琍一人分别出演三个角色。<ref>{{cite web |url=http://ent.china.com/zh_cn/movie/news/205/20050828/12607255.html |title=张黎开拍新片《锦衣卫》 马伊俐一人饰三角(图) |date=2005-08-23 |accessdate=2014-03-08 |work=中国网 |archive-date=2014-04-07 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20140407080059/http://ent.china.com/zh_cn/movie/news/205/20050828/12607255.html |dead-url=no }}</ref>

该剧耗费人民币2000万元，拍摄地在[[北京市|北京市]]。<ref name="cat">{{cite web |url=http://ent.sina.com.cn/x/2007-07-16/01361639139.shtml |title=每周电视质量报告——电视剧《锦衣卫》新说成胡说 |date=2007-07-16 |accessdate=2014-03-08 |work=新浪 |archive-date=2020-09-06 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20200906134910/http://ent.sina.com.cn/x/2007-07-16/01361639139.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>

==播出==
该片收视率很低，而且由于过分不尊重历史事实，导致被观众批评“违背史实”，<ref name="bull">{{cite web |url=http://cul.sohu.com/20070723/n251193440.shtml |title=电视剧《锦衣卫》不尊重史实 引起观众诟病 |date=2007-07-23 |accessdate=2014-03-08 |work=搜狐 |archive-date=2016-03-04 |archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20160304224006/http://cul.sohu.com/20070723/n251193440.shtml |dead-url=no }}</ref>导演张黎回应说“这是一部商业剧”。<ref>{{cite web|url=http://www.china.com.cn/culture/txt/2007-07/24/content_8570881.htm|title=张黎：《锦衣卫》纯属商业片|date=2007-07-24|accessdate=2014-03-08|work=中国网|archive-date=2019-06-03|archive-url=https://web.archive.org/web/20190603075420/http://www.china.com.cn/culture/txt/2007-07/24/content_8570881.htm|dead-url=no}}</ref>

